title: Total United States vehicles entering in Canada 2019
summary: The graph shows the trend of the Total Number of United States States vehicles to Canada during the year 2019 .
The Number drops between January and February shows the minimum value in February .
From February on it increases and shows the maximum value in August .
gold: This chart shows the monthly total US vehicles entering Canada in 2019 . The data range from around 0.6  10^6 to 1.2  10^6 . The trend generally increased from January to August and decreased thereafter , with from April to July having almost linear increase .
